<div class="container">
  <h1>Lets Talk</h1>


  <h3>Common reasons people reach out:</h3>
  

  <ul>

    <li><span>Press Releases:</span> Press releases can be sent to our marketing team by filling out the form 
      below. Simply include the URL where the press release can be found.</li>
    <li><span>Enquire About A Car:</span> We know it is impossible to stay up to date on every new concept.</li>
    <li><span>Advertising Enquiries:</span> If you are looking to reach our network, we recommend that you 
      complete the form with all your relevant information.</li>
    <li><span>Something Else?</span> No worries. Fill out the form below and weâ€™ll get back to you soon.</li>   
    
  </ul>

  <%= form_for @contact do |f| %>
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <%= f.label :name %></br>
      <%= f.text_field :name, required: true, class: "contact-form-text-area" %></br>

      <%= f.label :email %></br>
      <%= f.text_field :email, required: true, class: "contact-form-text-area" %></br>

      <%= f.label :message %></br>
      <%= f.text_area :message, rows: 8, cols: 50, required: true, class: "contact-form-text-area", 
            placeholder: "Write your enquiry or message here"%></br>

     

      <%= f.submit 'Send Message', class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
    </div>
  <% end %>

  
 
</div>


